And I prefer to stick around.

251
00:12:06,350 --> 00:12:08,980
雷米·丹顿  专情男子
Remy Danton, serial monogamist.

252
00:12:09,770 --> 00:12:10,820
你是在开玩笑吗
This a joke?

253
00:12:12,420 --> 00:12:16,880
抱歉  我不是...抱歉
I'm sorry. I didn't, uh... sorry.

254
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:27,090
如果你不是认真的  就不会有下一次了
This doesn't happen again unless it's leading somewhere.

255
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:29,350
