where these planes are coming from.

268
00:13:00,070 --> 00:13:01,510
我们认识联邦航空管理局的人吗
Who do we know in the FAA?

269
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:04,150
我不认识  但道尔认识  我让他去打探了
I don't know anyone. But Doyle does. I already got him on it.

270
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:05,910
有消息就通知你
I'll text you when I hear back from Doyle.

271
00:13:06,140 --> 00:13:07,080
我得走了
I gotta go.

272
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,500
要走了吗
You leaving?

273
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:18,450
是的  谢谢让我度过美好的一晚
Yeah. Thanks for last night.

274
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:21,440
