No promises. Just test the waters.

300
00:14:36,070 --> 00:14:36,690
我愿意去找他谈
I'm happy to do that.

301
00:14:36,690 --> 00:14:38,930
我和马特关系不错  我给他打个电话
I've got a good relationship with Matt. I'll call him.

302
00:14:38,930 --> 00:14:40,610
